<div class="badge">Email Verification</div>
<h1 class="title">Verify Your Email Address</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Please use this verification code to complete your account setup. Enter it in the verification form or click the button below.</p>

<div class="highlight-box">
  <div class="code">{{otp}}</div>
  <p style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; color: #737373; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;">
    This code expires in {{expiresIn}}
  </p>
</div>

{{#if actionUrl}}
{{> button url=actionUrl label="Verify Email Address"}}
{{/if}}

<div class="security-info">
  <strong>Security Notice:</strong> Never share this verification code with anyone. DeployIO will never ask for your verification code via phone or email.
</div>

<p style="color: #737373; margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px;">
  If you didn't request this verification code, you can safely ignore this email. Your account will remain secure.
</p>